title: (Tues Early Bird) Bobby’s Top 5 Songs NOT to Sing At Karaoke + Morgan’s Thirst Trap Challenge + Caller Sets the Story Straight on Alleged “Shady” First Date
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Bobby’s Top 5 Songs NOT to Sing At Karaoke + Morgan’s Thirst Trap Challenge + Caller Sets the Story Straight on Alleged “Shady” First Date
description:
Bobby shares his list of banned songs from karaoke and the reasoning why. Morgan has the men on the show pick between two celebrities based on which is more attractive in their eyes. Remember the story where we were wondering if a listener was going on a first date to Bobby’s comedy show with a married guy? Well, he calls in and sets the story straight!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
